1
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:38,720
♪The waves of sword dance send out ripples♪

2
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:41,560
♪I weather the raging storm to chase after the victorious banner♪

3
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,920
♪The snow is not concerned with joy or sadness♪

4
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:47,920
♪The horse rein I have been holding falls apart in the desert♪

5
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:51,040
♪My greenness is not an excuse to be bullied♪

6
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:54,200
♪Spreading the wings and soaring, inviting recklessness at any moment♪

7
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,200
♪I do not fear the life of hardship♪

8
00:00:57,280 --> 00:01:00,040
♪For I shall solve all riddles destined for me♪

9
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:03,400
♪Great difficulties can summon the sea of courage♪

10
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:06,640
♪It's worth defending heroic spirits in the martial arts world♪

11
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:12,000
♪One smile is all it takes, I travel faraway with my spirited ballads♪

12
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:15,820
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

13
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,880
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,000
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

15
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:25,000
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

16
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:28,320
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

17
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,080
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

18
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:38,040
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

19
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,760
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

20
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,760
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

21
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,680
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

22
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:50,400
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

23
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:53,120
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

24
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:56,000
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:03,480
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 9]

28
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:30,280
Great!

29
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,710
You finally woke up.

30
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:33,280
Xiaohua.

31
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,190
Xiaohua.

32
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:36,840
[Death is Life]

33
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,240
Isn't...

34
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,150
Isn't this from the dream?

35
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,000
How come it's here?

36
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,680
It's the tip I gave you.

37
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,240
When I arrived,

38
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,910
I noticed many peculiarities.

39
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,710
The entire manor

40
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,190
is shrouded in miasma.

41
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,910
And the poisonous miasma

42
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,310
pulled you into a dream.

43
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,520
Liuli Manor

44
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,000
houses many precious treasures.

45
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,630
The miasma

46
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,190
is a test it laid out.

47
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,190
It can create illusions,

48
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:06,430
drawing you into avaricious nightmares.

49
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,400
Only by seeing through the illusion

50
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,430
can you wake up

51
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:11,120
and stay in this manor

52
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,120
as an esteemed guest.

53
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,590
Before I passed out,

54
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,400
I recalled a trick taught by my master.

55
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:21,470
I kept sniffing the Sobering Incense,

56
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,960
but I still slept nonetheless.

57
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,710
Perhaps

58
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,360
the Sobering Incense took effect.

59
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:32,630
Before long,

60
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:33,800
I woke up.

61
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,240
I monitored both of your conditions

62
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,430
and thought of a book.

63
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:38,680
It said

64
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:39,800
that dreams

65
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,590
were the opposite of reality.

66
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,190
The more active you are in a dream,

67
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,360
the harder it is for you to wake up.

68
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,470
Instead,

69
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,750
you need to die in the dream...

70
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:48,030
Weigui!

71
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,030
... before you can wake up.

72
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:49,800
Lei Lingze!

73
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,400
- To wake you up, - Wake up.

74
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,120
I came up with this plan.

75
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,960
Only by killing yourself

76
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:55,910
in the dream

77
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,000
can you wake up.

78
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,560
Thank you, Miss Xiaohua.

79
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:02,910
Otherwise, we

80
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:04,150
would have died here.

81
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,240
There are only

82
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:07,310
the three of us here.

83
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,150
How come

84
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,470
the Divine Maiden

85
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,710
was in my dream?

86
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:12,590
Could it be that

87
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,360
she also came to the manor?

88
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:18,600
Perhaps.

89
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:20,630
We can't stay here for long.

90
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,240
Let's get out.

91
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,600
It's still day

92
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,870
but there is no one.

93
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,600
The miasma is gone too.

94
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:39,870
How was your rest, young heroes?

95
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:41,560
How was my rest?

96
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,270
Young Master Lin,

97
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,480
what is the meaning of this?

98
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,040
We saved you out of kindness.

99
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,310
Yet you poisoned us and put us to sleep.

100
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,240
Is this how you treat your guests?

101
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,000
This is a misunderstanding.

102
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,870
You just arrived at Liuli Manor.

103
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:56,040
You might need time to get used to the mist here,

104
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:57,830
so I handed out pillows

105
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,430
for you to rest properly.

106
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,390
I appreciate that.

107
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,510
We have things to attend to.

108
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,160
Farewell.

109
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,270
I...

110
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:05,800
Wait.

111
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,870
Halt.

112
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:13,630
Young Master,

113
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,920
the Skysplitter fragment is gone.

114
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,480
Young heroes,

115
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,480
the Skysplitter fragment

116
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,270
is the manor's prized possession.

117
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,270
I'll

118
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,600
have to explain this to my father.

119
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,830
I may need you to stay here to assist us

120
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,070
in the investigation.

121
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,190
What does your oversight have anything

122
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,270
to do with us?

123
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:44,750
Are you saying

124
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,950
we took your fragment?

125
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,600
Young Master Lin.

126
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,720
Ye.

127
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,800
I know them well.

128
00:05:58,270 --> 00:06:00,160
They will not do such a thing.

129
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,920
Ye, you are my father's esteemed guest.

130
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,560
But they are...

131
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,160
I can retrieve

132
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:09,000
the Skysplitter fragment with them.

133
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,310
It must be Tianwaitian's doing.

134
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,000
But...

135
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
Young Master Lin,

136
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:21,560
I understand your concerns.

137
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,160
I can stay here if you want.

138
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:23,750
Xiaohua!

139
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:27,510
I

140
00:06:28,310 --> 00:06:29,310
agree with you.

141
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,190
You

142
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,480
are the best candidate to stay back.

143
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,680
Miss Xiaohua.

144
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,040
Take care.

145
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,310
I'll count on all of you.

146
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,600
Let's go.

147
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,070
Hua Xiaohua.

148
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:02,600
Wait for us to come back.

149
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:22,720
Look.

150
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,800
Scattered footsteps.

151
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,120
There were many of them.

152
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:27,920
Take the shortcut.

153
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:00,920
What a coincidence.

154
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,480
Are you

155
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,600
trying to run away after stealing the Skysplitter fragment?

156
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:19,480
Come.

157
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,070
Give it back.

158
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,750
And I may

159
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,480
spare all of you.

160
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,430
Attack!

161
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:04,080
Run!

162
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,270
We got the fragment.

163
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:26,790
Weigui.

164
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:27,840
Are you okay?

165
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,670
Did you remember something?

166
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:51,360
Weigui.

167
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,000
Is your past

168
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,360
related to the Divine Maiden

169
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,550
and

170
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:58,080
the Skysplitter as well?

171
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,630
I'm not too sure.

172
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:10,550
Nevertheless,

173
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,270
do you

174
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,270
really think that once we gather

175
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:16,480
the Skysplitter fragments, we can have the Skysplitter?

176
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,670
No one knows if it's true or fake.

177
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,870
But ever since the Skysplitter fragments appeared,

178
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,960
there have been conflicts.

179
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:28,440
Each sect suffers heavy losses as they fight for the fragments.

180
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:30,030
And the common folks live in misery.

181
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,360
The imperial court doesn't care either.

182
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,080
No one knows for sure if the fragments can make the Skysplitter.

183
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:35,510
But the world

184
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,000
is indeed the worse for it.

185
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:38,870
Ye,

186
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,630
the Divine Maiden

187
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,200
said the same thing too.

188
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,270
Who?

189
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,000
Before you arrived

190
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,000
at Qingyin Parlor,

191
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,790
the Divine Maiden said the same thing.

192
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:50,750
Ye.

193
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,750
Have you met the Divine Maiden?

194
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,750
Do you know her?

195
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:55,510
We're running out of firewood.

196
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,550
I'll gather some.

197
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:57,750
Ye!

198
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,360
Oh,

199
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,510
Hua Xiaohua is stuck in Liuli Manor.

200
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,440
We must find a way

201
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,960
to save her tomorrow morning.

202
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:18,480
Also,

203
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,320
see if the Skysplitter fragment

204
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,000
triggers your memory or not.

205
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:23,870
It might solve the mystery of your past.

206
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,000
Think.

207
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,150
What can you remember?

208
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,320
I can't remember everything,

209
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,750
but I always see scenes from my childhood.

210
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:35,630
I have a feeling

211
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:37,910
that my father's death

212
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,550
has something to do with the Skysplitter.

213
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,870
And Xiao Se, the owner of the sword, once told me

214
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,870
that to find the Skysplitter, I must visit

215
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,320
the corridor.

216
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,320
- The corridor? - The corridor?

217
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,270
Do you remember where it is?

218
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,320
Not very clearly.

219
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:01,480
But

220
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,790
I remember roughly what it looks like.

221
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,390
Perhaps the sword

222
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,150
can lead us to Xiao Se

223
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,910
and my past.

224
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:11,550
Who's there?

225
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,510
It's me.

226
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:14,840
It's me.

227
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:16,910
Hua Xiaohua?

228
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,390
Am I hallucinating?

229
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,510
I'm real.

230
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,550
How did you escape?

231
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,870
Young Master Lin freed me.

232
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,750
He didn't want people to continue

233
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:28,670
coveting

234
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,120
the Skysplitter fragment he used to own.

235
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,000
He added

236
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,360
that if we found the fragment,

237
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:33,480
there was no need to return.

238
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,320
Then

239
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:37,120
why did we dream of the wedding ceremony with the ox-head butcher?

240
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:40,840
I heard that when the first owner of Liuli Manor got married,

241
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,960
his bride ran away.

242
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,790
He then became a laughing stock.

243
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,720
That might have something to do with your dream.

244
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,790
Then why go through the trouble?

245
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:51,150
He

246
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,510
could've given us the fragment

247
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,360
from the beginning.

248
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:55,240
He didn't want to cross his father for it,

249
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,120
but he also

250
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,480
wanted to protect Liuli Manor.

251
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,440
That's why he asked us not to return.

252
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:03,870
Then

253
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:05,790
where should we go next?

254
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:08,360
I think

255
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,790
we should find the corridor.

256
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,550
Let's spend a night here for now.

257
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,000
We depart tomorrow.

258
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:59,400
♪How can I make peace when time♪

259
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:02,520
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

260
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:07,480
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

261
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:10,760
♪Render me blind♪

262
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:15,680
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

263
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:18,960
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

264
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:23,920
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

265
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:27,080
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

266
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:30,080
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

267
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:32,360
♪But misunderstood♪

268
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:35,440
♪I do not know sincerity♪

269
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:40,200
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

270
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:43,520
♪Let's not meet again♪

271
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:46,480
♪No one will be able to understand me♪

272
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,560
♪None will go as I wish♪

273
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:51,800
♪How I long for that one moment to last forever♪

274
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:56,520
♪All mortal obsessions turn into dusts of nothingness♪

275
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:59,720
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

276
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:03,400
♪Not in another life♪

277
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:37,560
♪How can I make peace when time♪

278
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:40,680
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

279
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:45,640
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

280
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:49,160
♪Render me blind♪

281
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:53,840
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

282
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:57,120
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

283
00:15:58,280 --> 00:16:02,080
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

284
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:05,240
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

285
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:08,240
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

286
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:10,520
♪But misunderstood♪

